{"tid":2042541,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄭若驊︰特朗普指中國將香港變「一國一制」說法非常錯","createTime":"2020-05-30T01:23:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T02:06:04.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fefcb632fbfdf30092334898f4dd491949015823","tid":2042541,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T01:23:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1529255_1_20200530090920.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1529255_1_20200530090920.jpg&h=427dcde9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n律政司司長鄭若驊認為，美國總統特朗普指責中國將香港「一國兩制」變成「一國一制」，是非常錯的說法。<br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊出席本台節目《星期六問責》時說，中央一直以「一國」原則處理香港事務，中央建立「港區國安法」是天公地道，合法、合情、合憲。她又說，根據國際法原則，干擾其他國家的事務是不能接受。<br />\n<br />\n對於特朗普表示將採取措施制裁參與削弱香港自治的香港官員，鄭若驊被問到會否擔心自己被制裁，她說，香港官員沒有削弱香港的高度自治，國家安全從來都不是香港內部事務，又說要視乎美方有何具體措施才能較好回答有關問題。"},{"pid":"dd7ebb263ab1b97e2f9f2f4ef5b7f872fe99f762","tid":2042541,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T01:23:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529255-20200530.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529255-20200530.htm&d=MUobR5x4uSQxHz8Khhk%2FvMemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=e3314303\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529255-20200530.htm&h=bbf13623\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529255-20200530.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2998d9309a7b43cc775163ff9fd096ee756218fe","tid":2042541,"uid":16029,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T01:23:41.000Z","msg":"你岩曬啦肥西"},{"pid":"a48ed2a3dc496eedeeb168cc8995cd5851188996","tid":2042541,"uid":155095,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T01:25:06.000Z","msg":"送中受害者 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\